  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>This wooden pole is plain, save that green dragon scales adorn to its length. Treated as a +2 quarterstaff, it is a favorite of Irori's wandering followers. In the hands of a worshiper of Irori, a quarterstaff of contemplation gains the ki intensifyingUE weapon special ability. If the wielder is a follower of Irori and possesses the wholeness of body class feature, he can spend a full-round action to meditate using the staff as a focus. Treat this as using wholeness of body at the cost of 1 ki point instead of 2.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> +2 quarterstaff</p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Magic Arms and Armor, creator must be a 7th-level monk</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Inner Sea Combat",
